punjab 1984 ( punjabi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2014 indian punjabi period drama film directed by anurag singh . it is based on the &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; punjab insurgency 's impact on social life , notably it is a story of a mother and her missing son . starring diljit dosanjh and kirron kher , the film is the fourth collaboration between director singh and actor dosanjh . punjab 1984 released on 27 june 2014 to excellent box office collections .